public static java.lang.String sendToDB(java.lang.String category,

                                        java.lang.String special_info,

This method processes a request to add an item to the database It calls the Create.php file with the given parameters

Parameters:
category - The category selected by the user
location - The location of the object if it is not in a building
fid - The floor ID of the object if it IS in a building
special_info - Currently ignored: Include any special info
bb - If category is school supplies, "bb" indicates blue books at location
sc - If category is school supplies, "sc" indicates scantrons at location
print - If category is school supplies, "print" indicates printing at location
Returns:
A String indicating if the request was successful
